VI TIPS:
select = command mode 'v', select text with arrows, 'y' (=yank), to paste 'p' 
select text, press ':' then enter 's/^/  /' this substitutess 's/' spaces '/   /' for each line's beginning '^'
gg = begin, G = einde, v = select, V = selecteer regel, u=lowercase, U= Uppercase
--> to convert document to lower- or uppercase: ggVGu of ggVGU

